Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:36.65,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}We gangsters will raise a flag of rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:54.51,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The rage in our souls that erases any sense of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:02:01.47,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Has been with us since we swore to defy God's diabolical plan
