Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.16,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Together we will stand up against this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.75,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}In which despair breeds despair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.88,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't care! I have no need for mercy
